snippet.title: Skinned Locust
snippet.description:
Welcome to SkinnedLocust. This channel is dedicated to all things horrifying and scary including true horror stories from reddit users and subscribers. Stay tuned for at least 3 new videos every week. 

Submit your stories to SkinnedLocust@gmail.com
